<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>SNUGYM</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../css/intro.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header-logo">
            <a href="/users/newx">
                <img src="../assets/whitelogo.png">
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="header-buttons">
            <button class="button-activated">
                <a href="/users/new" style="color: white; text-decoration: none">메인</a>
            </button>
            <button>
                공지
            </button>
            <button>
                문의
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class ="header-login">
            <button>
                <a href="/sessions/new" style="text-decoration: none; color: white">로그인</a>
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="header-search">
            <button>
                <img src="../assets/whitesearch.png" alt="search icon"/>
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="header-instagram">
            <button>
                <img src="../assets/instagram 2.png">
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <div class="main-login">
            <img src="../assets/gympic11.png">
            <div style="white-space: nowrap;" class="main-login-left">
                <h1>
                    이제는 <br>
                    정착할 시간이에요.
                </h1>
                <div class="whiteline">
                </div>
                <h3>
                    헬스장, 필라테스, 그리고 요가까지 <br>
                    멀리 갈 필요는 없답니다.
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="main-login-right">
                <section>
                    <%= form_tag users_path do %>
                    <p>
                        아이디 <br>
                        <input type="text" name="name">
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        비밀번호 <br>
                        <input type="password" name="password">
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        비밀번호 확인 <br>
                        <input type="password" name="password_confirmation">
                    </p>
                    <h4>
                        <input type="submit" value="회원가입">
                        <div class="notice">
                            <%= flash[:alert] %><br>
                        </div>
                    </h4>
                    <% end %>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
